::Hevn::
       He nods again quietly.  "I don't know what else to tell you."  He 
reaches up and lifts her chin with his hand.  "If there's anything I can do 
for you, anything at all.  You need only to ask and it shall be done."  He 
smiles gently and watches her.  "Alright?"
